org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.definitions

Class VariableDefinition

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.definitions.DefinitionBase
      • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.definitions.VariableDefinition
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDefinition, IDocumentableDefinition, IVariableDefinition, IDefinitionSet
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConstantDefinition, ParameterDefinition

    public class VariableDefinition
extends DefinitionBase
implements IVariableDefinition
    Instances of this class represent definitions of ActionScript variables and constants in the symbol table.

    After a variable definition is in the symbol table, it should always be accessed through the read-only IVariableDefinition interface.
